      "content": "\"letting go of the burden\"... i dont know. it sounds almost peaceful when you say it like that. but it's scary too. i feel like im just waiting for my body to finally give up on me, just stuck in this waiting room. it feels so much more dignified to have some kind of say in it, rather than just fading away bit by bit.",
